						<div class="wxbox_left">
							<div class="wx_text">
								<div class="wx_text_line highlight"> Your mobile hiring home page has been generated </div>
								<div class="wx_text_line"> Please scan two-dimensional code attention “<if condition="C('qscms_weixin_mpname')">{:C('qscms_weixin_mpname')}<else />{:C('qscms_site_name')}</if>” No public ，</div>
